<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Features ‚Äì <%= appName %></title>
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    :root { --bg:#0f1117; --bg2:#1a1d27; --bg3:#21262d; --border:#2a2d3a; --text:#e6edf3; --muted:#8b949e; --blue:#3b82f6; --blue-light:#60a5fa; }
    body { background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; }
    a { text-decoration: none; }
    nav { background: rgba(15,17,23,0.95); backdrop-filter: blur(10px); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100; }
    .nav-inner { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px; height: 64px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; }
    .nav-logo { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--blue-light); }
    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 24px; align-items: center; }
    .nav-links a { color: var(--muted); font-size: 14px; }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--text); }
    .btn-nav { background: var(--blue); color: white !important; padding: 8px 20px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 14px; }
    .nav-links a.nav-active {
      color: var(--text) !important;
      background: rgba(59,130,246,0.12);
      padding: 5px 11px;
      border-radius: 7px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(59,130,246,0.25);
    }
    .page { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 80px 24px; }
    .page-hero { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 80px; }
    .page-hero h1 { font-size: 42px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .page-hero p { font-size: 18px; color: var(--muted); max-width: 520px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .features-big { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 60px; }
    .feature-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 60px; align-items: center; }
    .feature-row:nth-child(even) .feat-text { order: 2; }
    .feature-row:nth-child(even) .feat-visual { order: 1; }
    .feat-text .label { font-size: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: var(--blue-light); margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: 600; }
    .feat-text h2 { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .feat-text p { color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .feat-text ul { list-style: none; }
    .feat-text ul li { color: var(--muted); font-size: 14px; padding: 4px 0; }
    .feat-text ul li::before { content: '‚úì '; color: #22c55e; font-weight: bold; }
    .feat-visual { background: var(--bg2); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 14px; padding: 32px; min-height: 200px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 64px; }
    /* Footer handled by shared public-footer partial */
    footer a { color: var(--blue-light); }
    @media (max-width: 768px) { .feature-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .feature-row:nth-child(even) .feat-text { order: 0; } .feature-row:nth-child(even) .feat-visual { order: 0; } }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<nav>
  <div class="nav-inner">
    <a href="/" class="nav-logo"><%= appName %></a>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="/features" style="color:var(--text);">Features</a>
      <a href="/pricing">Pricing</a>
      <a href="/about">About</a>
      <a href="/security">Security</a>
      <a href="/login" class="btn-nav">Sign In</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</nav>
<div class="page">
  <div class="page-hero">
    <h1>Everything Built In</h1>
    <p>A complete temperature compliance platform ‚Äî no plugins, no integrations, no extras needed.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="features-big">
    <div class="feature-row">
      <div class="feat-text">
        <div class="label">Live Monitoring</div>
        <h2>See your entire fleet in real time</h2>
        <p>The Live page shows every active driver, their last temperature reading, and how long ago they logged. Vehicles overdue for logging are flagged automatically.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Overdue detection based on configurable timeout</li>
          <li>Out-of-range temperature highlighting</li>
          <li>Driver name and vehicle registration</li>
          <li>Office TV monitor board for wall display</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="feat-visual">üì°</div>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-row">
      <div class="feat-text">
        <div class="label">Compliance Sheets</div>
        <h2>Automated weekly compliance records</h2>
        <p>Every week a full compliance sheet is generated automatically ‚Äî no manual data entry. Drivers sign on their device, admins countersign digitally, and the sheet is locked.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Landscape A4 PDF format</li>
          <li>Driver + admin signature capture</li>
          <li>Odometer tracking</li>
          <li>Sheet locked and tamper-evident after sign-off</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="feat-visual">üìã</div>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-row">
      <div class="feat-text">
        <div class="label">Audit &amp; Compliance</div>
        <h2>Full audit trail for every action</h2>
        <p>Every login, log entry, vehicle change, and role update is recorded in the workspace event console with timestamps, user attribution, and metadata.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Colour-coded event console</li>
          <li>Filter by date, user, action type</li>
          <li>custom automatic retention</li>
          <li>Exportable for external audits</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="feat-visual">üñ•</div>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-row">
      <div class="feat-text">
        <div class="label">Multi-Asset Management</div>
        <h2>Manage multiple operations independently</h2>
        <p>The platform administrator creates and manages workspaces for different companies, depots, or clients. Each workspace is completely isolated with its own staff, vehicles, and settings.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Full platform control from your admin dashboard</li>
          <li>Per-workspace staff and vehicle limits</li>
          <li>Custom branding per workspace</li>
          <li>Independent timezone and compliance settings</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="feat-visual">üè¢</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<%- include('../partials/public-footer') %>
</body>
</html>
